#. type: group
#: emacs-lisp-intro.texi:21203 emacs-lisp-intro.texi:21704
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Optionally, VERTICAL-STEP, a positive integer,\n"
"specifies how much a Y axis label increments for\n"
"each line.  For example, a step of 5 means that\n"
