#. type: group
#: emacs-lisp-intro.texi:21213 emacs-lisp-intro.texi:21714
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Optionally, HORIZONTAL-STEP, a positive integer,\n"
"specifies how much an X  axis label increments for\n"
"each column.\"\n"
"  (let* ((symbol-width (length graph-blank))\n"
